            "title": "港股開跌183點新股搶鏡 群核飆逾1.71倍  商湯挫2.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開跌183點或0.68%，報26210，恒生科技指數跌36點或0.72%，報5055，恒生國企指數跌64點或0.72%，報8840點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交47.44億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：群核科技官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Manycore-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：群核科技官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Manycore-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：群核科技官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩新股一枝獨秀，長光辰芯(03277)升80.54%，報72，成交居首 ; 群核(00068)升171.65%，報20.7元，成交居第二位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">平保(02318)跌1.04%，報62元，成交居第三。友邦(01299)跌1.6%，報82.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">商湯(00020) 折讓8.61%配股，作價1.91元，今早開跌2.39%，報2.04元。阿里(09988)跌0.59%，報135元 ; 美團(03690)跌1.41%，報87.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">贛鋒(01772)預告虧轉盈，開升1.01%，報85元 ; 天齊(09696)升2.65%，報58.15元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15883809-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e8%b7%8c183%e9%bb%9e%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e6%90%b6%e9%8f%a1-%e7%be%a4%e6%a0%b8%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be1-71%e5%80%8d-%e5%95%86%e6%b9%af%e6%8c%ab2-4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240420240415_FI_source-web_HKSTOCK.png.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 09:34:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "贛鋒鋰業盈喜   預告虧轉盈賺16億至21億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">贛鋒鋰業(01772)盈喜，預期截至3月底止首季股東應佔淨利潤介乎16億至21億元(人民幣‧下同)；該公司2025年度同期錄得股東應佔虧損3.56億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231206_FI_source-web_01772.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231206_FI_source-web_01772.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">贛鋒鋰業指出，預期虧轉盈，主要由於下游客戶對鋰鹽的需求強勁增長，公司鋰鹽產品的銷售價格按年有較大幅度上漲；此外，公司鋰資源項目的產能釋放，公司成本結構不斷優化；加上動力電池及儲能產業市場持續增長，鋰電池板塊產銷量明顯提升，故經營業績增長。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，公司持有的PLS Group Ltd(PLS)股票價格上漲產生公允價值變動收益，在領式期權相關的既定風險管理策略對沖後，整體公允價值變動收益約2.59億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15883793-%e8%b4%9b%e9%8b%92%e9%8b%b0%e6%a5%ad%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e9%a0%90%e5%91%8a%e8%99%a7%e8%bd%89%e7%9b%88%e8%b3%ba16%e5%84%84%e8%87%b321%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 09:24:19",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
