        {
            "title": "812萬購將軍澳維景灣畔2房戶  一手業主2004年買入 物業升值逾2倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15880395&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">利嘉閣地產將軍澳都會駅分行促成將軍澳維景灣畔9座高層D室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約498方呎，屬2房間隔，望市景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據悉，原業主2004年以約258.8萬元一手購入，持貨至今轉售，帳面獲利逾553萬元，期內物業升值約2.1倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該屋苑目前放盤量約25個，最低入場費由約700萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880395-812%e8%90%ac%e8%b3%bc%e5%b0%87%e8%bb%8d%e6%be%b3%e7%b6%ad%e6%99%af%e7%81%a3%e7%95%942%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6-%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb2004%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%b7%e5%85%a5-%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%ad%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 09:12:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "THE CAMPTON 中層1房戶620萬元成交   原業主持貨6 年虧蝕157萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15880372&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">香港置業西九龍四小龍分行促成一宗THE CAMPTON買賣成交，中層一房單位獲同區首置客以 620萬元 承接，實用呎價約 16062元，屬市價成交。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述單位為THE CAMPTON 中層Q室，實用面積約386平方呎，屬1房間隔，原業主以708萬元放售後獲同區客洽詢，雙方經議價後以620萬元成交，實用呎價約16062元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據悉，新買家故睇樓1次後決定承接上述單位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">資料顯示，原業主於2020年6月以約777.7萬元購入上述單位。是次轉手業主帳面虧損157萬元離場。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880372-the-campton-%e4%b8%ad%e5%b1%a41%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6620%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a86-%e5%b9%b4%e8%99%a7%e8%9d%95157%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 09:12:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "荃灣樂悠居2房620萬元成交   持貨4個月升值13%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15880336&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 中原地產荃灣柏傲灣分行新近促成荃灣樂悠居中層5室成交，實用面積420平方呎，兩房間隔，叫價638萬元，減價18萬元，以620萬元易手，實用呎價14762元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原業主於2025年12月以550萬元買入，持貨約4個月，賬面獲利70萬元或12.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880336-%e8%8d%83%e7%81%a3%e6%a8%82%e6%82%a0%e5%b1%852%e6%88%bf620%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a84%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc13",
